      "date": "2012-11-27 16:41:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(1 inline comment)\n\nFor FAILURE_MODE=HARD, if MDT0 and MDT1 are on the same node, then those two MDTs will be failed over at the same time. So, we need add some check to make sure that MDT0 and MDT1 are on different nodes while FAILURE_MODE=HARD, otherwise skip the test.\n\nSince those tests will be skipped by autotest now, it's better to upload a manual test run result with multiple MDTs to make sure that the tests pass.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
